{"lemma":"حَلَقاتِ","slug":"حَلَقاتِ","root":"ح.ل.ق","root_slug":"ح-ل-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ل-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n8873","n8874","n8875","n8876"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ring, loop","examples":[{"text":"حلقة مطاطية مانعة للتسرب\nLeakage rubber، rubber sealing ring"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"link of a chain"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"show; episode (single edition of a serial program)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"circle of people (e.g. for discussion, studying)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ring (as jewellery)","tags":["rare"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ħa.la.qa/","/ħal.qa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8873","headword_ar":"حَلْقَةٌ","root":"Hlq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A single act of shaving"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. One says to a beloved child, when he belches,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqapF wakaborapF","text_ar":"حَلْقَةً وَكَبْرَةً"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa$aHomapF fiY Als~ur~api","text_ar":"وَشَحْمَةً فِى السُّرَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May thy head be shaven time after time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, K, *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that thou mayest grow old,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, TA,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and acquire fat at the navel:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mayest thou be preserved so as to have thy head shaven, and to grow old."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.)       -A2-  As meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A ring;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anything circular;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqp","text_ar":"حلقة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of iron, and of silver, and of gold; (TA;) a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqp","text_ar":"حلقة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a coat of mail, &c.; (Mgh;) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqp","text_ar":"حلقة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a door; and a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqp","text_ar":"حلقة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of people; (S, K;) in this last instance meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a ring"},{"kind":"text","text":"of people; (Msb, TA;) it is also with fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"l","text_ar":"ل"},{"kind":"text","text":"; i. e. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalaqapN","text_ar":"حَلَقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Mgh, Msb, K;) mentioned by Yoo, on the authority of Aboo-'Amr Ibn-El-'Alà, (S, Msb,) and with kesr; (K;) i. e. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaliqapN","text_ar":"حَلِقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; mentioned by Fr and El-Umawee, as of the dial. of Belhárith Ibn-Kaab; accord. to the O; or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiloqapN","text_ar":"حِلْقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to the L: (TA:) or there is no such word as ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalaqapN","text_ar":"حَلَقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) in chaste speech, (TA,) except as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAliqN","text_ar":"حَالِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) accord. to Aboo-'Amr Esh-Sheybánee; (S;) or it is a dial. var. of weak authority; (K;) accord. to Th, allowed by all, though of weak authority; (S;) or it is used by poetic license; (Mgh:) Lh says that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqp","text_ar":"حلقة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a door is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqapN","text_ar":"حَلْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalaqapN","text_ar":"حَلَقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; Kr says the same of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqp","text_ar":"حلقة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a company of men; Lth says that it is the former in this case, but that some say the latter; A 'Obeyd prefers the latter in the case of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqp","text_ar":"حلقة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of iron, but allows the former; and prefers the former in the case of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqp","text_ar":"حلقة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of people, but allows the latter; and Abu-l-'Abbás prefers the former in both cases, but allows the latter: (L:) the pl. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalaqN","text_ar":"حَلَقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) which is anomalous in relation to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqapN","text_ar":"حَلْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) or [rather] a quasipl. n., (TA,) but regular in relation to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalaqapN","text_ar":"حَلَقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) [as a coll. gen. n.,] like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSabN","text_ar":"قَصَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in relation to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSabapN","text_ar":"قَصَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and, (K,) accord. to As, (S,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HilaqN","text_ar":"حِلَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqapN","text_ar":"حَلْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqp","text_ar":"حلقة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of men and of iron, (TA,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bidarN","text_ar":"بِدَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badorapN","text_ar":"بَدْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiSaEN","text_ar":"قِصَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSoEapN","text_ar":"قَصْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) or this is a regular pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiloqapN","text_ar":"حِلْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalaqaAtN","text_ar":"حَلَقَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AA,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":630},{"kind":"text","text":"Yoo, S, K,) which is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalaqapN","text_ar":"حَلَقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HilaqaAtN","text_ar":"حِلَقَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) which is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiloqapN","text_ar":"حِلْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HilaAqN","text_ar":"حِلَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in relation to a company of men. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AinotazaEotu Haloqatahu","text_ar":"اِنْتَزَعْتُ حَلْقَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I pulled off his ring"},{"kind":"text","text":"], meaning, (app., Ibn-'Abbád,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I outwent him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preceded him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAlHaloqapi Almuforagapi","text_ar":"كَالحَلْقَةِ المُفْرَغَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Like the solid and continuous ring"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: a prov., applied to a company of men united in words and action. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DarabuwA","text_ar":"ضَرَبُوا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buyuwtahumo HilaAqFA","text_ar":"بُيُوتَهُمْ حِلَاقًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They pitched their tents in one series,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to form a ring"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rings"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: the last word being a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqapN","text_ar":"حَلْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HlqapN","text_ar":"حلقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuhiYa Eani AlHilaqi","text_ar":"نُهِىَ عَنِ الحِلَقِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabola AlS~alaApi","text_ar":"قَبْلَ الصَّلَاةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rings"},{"kind":"text","text":"of men [sitting in the mosque"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before prayer are forbidden"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqataA Alr~aHimi","text_ar":"حَلْقَتَا الرَّحِمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The two rings of the womb"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: one of these is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the mouth of the vulva, at its extremity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the meatus of the vagina:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and the other is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that which closes upon the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA='","text_ar":"مَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seminal fluid"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and opens for the menstrual discharge;"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the os uteri:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (K:) or, as some say, the other is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that whence the urine is emitted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the meatus urinarius:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but the former is the right explanation: and hence] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA='","text_ar":"مَا=ء"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~uTofapu fiY Haloqapi Alr~aHimi","text_ar":"النُّطْفَةُ فِى حَلْقَةِ الرَّحِمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The seminal fluid fell into the entrance of the womb."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haloqapu Ald~uburi","text_ar":"حَلْقَةُ الدُّبُرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The anus;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HitaAruhu","text_ar":"حِتَارُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arajuhu","text_ar":"شَرَجُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$rj","text_ar":"شرج"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtamN","text_ar":"خَاتَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence but two.] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqapN","text_ar":"حَلْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A brand upon camels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a round form, like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqp","text_ar":"حلقة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ring"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a door."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A coat of mail:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[because made of rings:] (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coats of mail:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arms,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weapons, in general,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and coats of mail, and the like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~akumo","text_ar":"اـِنَّكُمْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aholu AlHaloqapi wAlHuSuwni","text_ar":"اَهْلُ الحَلْقَةِ والحُصُونِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily ye are people of the coat of mail,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and of fortresses"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A rope."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b6-  And, of a vessel, (AZ, K,) and of a watering-trough, (AZ,) (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion that remains vacant after one has put in it somewhat"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of food or beverage, up to the half;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion that is above the half"},{"kind":"text","text":"being thus called: (AZ:) [or] of a wateringtrough, (tropical:)  the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fulness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"less than that."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Aboo-Málik, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waf~ayotu Haloqapa AlHawoDi","text_ar":"وَفَّيْتُ حَلْقَةَ الحَوْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_inaA='a","text_ar":"الاـِنَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I filled up the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqp","text_ar":"حلقة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the watering-trough"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the vessel"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (AZ, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","TA","K","Mgh","L","M","AZ"]},{"entry_id":"n8874","headword_ar":"حِلْقَةٌ","root":"Hlq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqapN","text_ar":"حَلْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n8875","headword_ar":"حَلَقَةٌ","root":"Hlq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqapN","text_ar":"حَلْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n8876","headword_ar":"حَلِقَةٌ","root":"Hlq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqapN","text_ar":"حَلْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}